(2, 'students', 'Students', '<div class=\"content-page\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You Are Just A Step Away For Starting A Promising Career With Us. Congratulation. You Can Make It. Our determined and dedicated professionals have made us the most reputed, recognized and respected Accounting Firm of UK. We have now realized the real value of professionals through years of experience. They are no lesser than our systems and the processes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The vision of our founders is to “Produce Leaders for Tomorrow”, therefore professional growth and training of students is on top of our priority list.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We thrive on creating a productive environment to enlighten the students with growth, development, insightful learning and in making them actualize their potential. Our focus is not only on your professional career, but your studies will also benefit from the practical insights and client exposure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We always have our door open for passionate, serious and hardworking students aiming at “Leading the Corporate World”. Besides the utility for them, this allows us to facilitate the high-quality accountancy services.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What do we Expect from You?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We recruit dynamic and creative employees. Your knowledge, talent and skills for multiple fields can win you a place at our company. You should be a visionary person with an out-of-the-box thinking approach. We admire the employees owning the goals, functions and responsibilities of the organization. Show your entrepreneurial spirit, and you are right for us. If you possess all of these traits, don’t wait, we want to have you!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Please send your CV at \r\n  <a href=\"mailto:careers@weaccountax.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\">careers@mintaccountax.co.uk</a>.\r\n</p></div>', 'Students carreer at MintAccountax', 'students at MintAccountax', '2020-01-03 12:14:22', '2020-01-03 15:01:40'),
(3, 'graduate', 'Graduate', '<div class=\"content-page\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>The Human Power will let us achieve our massive milestones. We always work to produce Leaders for the Future… You have what can make a Difference!</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The environment of our company will compliment your career growth and professional development. If you are a fresh graduate heading for a bright future or are you an experienced professional, you will get everything you are looking for.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Graduate here and you will have a bundle of experience of dealing live with clients and will also be exposed to the working world under our competent and acclaimed Accountancy Firm.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Our Culture</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You will enjoy personal development in our culture influenced by experts, experienced and admired professionals. You can also make a strong basis of your career with us in your field, which could be Accounts, Tax and Finance. You will unleash your talent and will embrace growth in our supportive and productive culture.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Expectations from the Trainees</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We expect you to play your part in realizing our goals in various disciplines with honour and integrity. You should exhibit problem-solving and pressure-tackling skills against complications.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We want you to have a thirst for learning and responsive instinct for the challenges imposed by the Industry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You are on the right path if you want to drive your career to success and love to work a portfolio of clients. Be a part of our largest firm.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We make sure to produce the best working conditions for your growth, leading to motivation for work and retention with us. If you have decided to take a bigger step, contact us through the website.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Please send your CV at <strong>careers@mintaccountax.co.uk</strong></p></div>', 'Mint Accountax is the appropriate fit for you as a graduate, whether you\'re just starting out or seeking for a new opportunity. Release your potential and embrace progress with the help', 'Graduate students at MintAccountax', '2020-01-03 12:15:31', '2022-06-09 15:43:42'),
(4, 'professional-experience', 'Professional Experience', '<p>Professional Experience<br></p>', 'Utilize your productive skills at right place and seek out professional experience. Build a solid foundation for your career with us in your profession, such as accounting, taxation,', 'Professional Experience', '2020-01-06 16:20:56', '2022-06-09 15:41:25'),
(5, 'growth-at-mintaccountax', 'Growth at MintAccountax', '<div class=\"content-page\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Your time at our Accounting Firm will prove fruitful whether you are a freshman or an experienced professional. You will learn from the exposure of working with and for International Clients. Learning communication, problem-solving and networking skills is another plus.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Culture:</strong> </h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Culture in our organization is open by default. There will be no barriers to communication with seniors in the office. This welcoming nature proves excellent for both the employees and the organization.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Global Perspective:</strong>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our international clients flavour us in maintaining and following the global corporate culture. Employees embrace instant decision-making skills in this regard while facing any challenge. International standards bring growth and positivity in us.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Team Work:</strong> </h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our Accounting Firm is known for Team-work. Warmth in our culture appreciates and motivates the employees to work collectively for the organizational goal. Collective work is always more efficient and effective.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Work-Life Balance:</strong> </h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Balance is what lets one grow. Our organizational is designed in a way to assist and help the employees in maintaining a healthy balance between professional and personal life.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Self-Value:</strong> </h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You will realize the real value you are adding to the organization while working with us an employee. We delegate tasks and responsibilities for grooming and learning on how to deal with your clients.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Growth:</strong> </h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We will you let grow in terms of Creativity, Professionalism and Skills. You may notice a significant improvement in your working as you keep working in the organization.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Performance-based Rewards:</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The only yardstick for measurement and appreciation at our company is your performance. We do not let your hard work go in vain. Instead, you will be rewarded for your productive work. Ace in the functions assigned to you and win whopping prizes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Your life in our accounting firm would be a perfect blend of the friendly work environment, learning and challenging and complicated tasks. Rewards and gifts for your performance motivate and ensures learning.</strong></p></div>', 'How you can improve your growth at MintAccountax in accounting career??', 'Growth at MintAccountax', '2020-01-06 16:30:58', '2020-01-06 16:30:58');

