ou devised the strategies for the matter, we will analyse them, fill in the gaps, correct the mistakes, and execute them to perfection.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p></div>', 'Real Estate and Construction', 'Real Estate and Construction', '2019-09-10 22:10:27', '2021-08-17 19:08:03'),
(9, 'Health Care Services', 'Health Care Services', '<div class=\"content-page\"><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">For every humane society, the optimal level of health is essential to living the highest standards of life and maintain the optimal quality of life. When we talk about the health, it is the protection and mental and physical well-being of the human beings. The health is ensured by implementing timely diagnosis, treatment, and the prevention techniques. The prevention techniques are applied for the multiple factors such as illness, injury, diseases, or any other ailment in terms of physical or mental health.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">The health care services are provided by the doctors, nurses, surgeons, physicians, psychologists, dentists, and pharmacists. However, as far as the activities are concerned, they include primary as well as secondary activities in terms of health and care. But what are the primary and secondary health care activities? Let us give you an overview to clear things out!<o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 15pt 0cm 7.5pt; font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\">Primary Health Care</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">This is the low level of services, or we may quote it as the necessary health care activities. The primary health care covers the general practitioner, physicians, pharmacist, nurse, and the physiotherapist. In other words, primary health care covers the consultation part of the diseases.<o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 15pt 0cm 7.5pt; font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\">Secondary Health Care</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">This is the high level of services that are usually comprised of intricate and complicated health services. The secondary health care comprises of cardiologists, urologists, endodontists, surgeons, dental specialists, medical specialists, and other health professionals. These doctors usually don’t get in touch with the patients during the initial consultation sessions. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 15pt 0cm 7.5pt; font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\">The Challenges</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">When it comes to the healthcare service provision, the industry is facing colossal challenges such as the varying government regulations. The main reason is that International Financial Reporting Standards is increasing the accountability and public challenges such as the scrutiny. In addition to the government regulations, the healthcare and medical industry are needful to adapt to the frequent medical innovations and acquire them to offer the highest standards of services in terms of the treatment. These technologies need to be present to ensure a competitive edge in the industry.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">At MintAccountax, we have offered our services to over 30 healthcare businesses, and through these services, we have managed to grasp extensive knowledge about the policies and regulations regarding accountancy and taxation in the industry. Through this expertise, we take pride in saying that we can aid the healthcare and medical industry with their accountancy and taxing needs without being a burden on their beds.<o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 15pt 0cm 7.5pt; font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\">Tax Relief &amp; Capital Allowance</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">The healthcare and medical industry are facing the financial crises in the United Kingdome, which is raising the issues of cash flow management and the ever-increasing competition. Moreover, the services’ rates are getting higher, which poses serious threats to the patients. However, there are multiple tax relief options during the financial crises that can be claimed. But the most healthcare clients are unaware of the options, and they don’t acquire the opportunity to claim the tax relief. However, at MintAccountax, we will provide the optimal level of services to ensure you get the deserved tax relief and the capital allowance.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">When you come to us, we will help you acquire the capital allowances inclusive of new – build surgery or extension and other qualifying costs and even certain professional fees that can be recovered. We guarantee that our team will be able to find and claim the maximum tax reliefs, and it will be profitable for your business. We will also take a look at the cash flow problems and streamline the solutions for that.<o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 15pt 0cm 7.5pt; font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\">Accounting and Bookkeeping Services</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">In addition to the industry-centric services, MintAccountax is offering the traditional accountancy services such as accounting and bookkeeping services for the healthcare clients of the United Kingdom.<o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 15pt 0cm 7.5pt; font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\">Tax Preparation &amp; Planning</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">Just like other industries, the healthcare industry is also ought to pay the taxes. If you need help with the taxes at MintAccountax, we are offering tax preparation services and the tax planning. On top of that, we are experienced enough to help in devising the capital gain and inheritance tax.<o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 15pt 0cm 7.5pt; font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\">Payroll Services</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-weight: normal;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">At MintAccountax, we understand the importance of timely salary and how it can affect the productivity of the employees. The healthcare industry is very demanding, and the employees need to be focused on. This is where our payroll services will help by optimizing the salary forwarding and keeping a record of it for the future use.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p></div>', 'Mint Accountax provides a variety of better health care services London with industry-specific compliance and advice services. Our team can help with various services such as tax compliance,', 'Better Health care Services London | Mint Accountax', '2019-09-10 22:10:57', '2022-06-09 15:19:05'),
(10, 'Education', 'Education', '<div class=\"content-page\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">I</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">t is needless to say that education plays an essential role in our lives and it’s a crucial part of every human being’s life. For adding quality of life to a person’s experience, education is an essential part of any civilization. Many people have a misconception that education revolves around the bookish knowledge and theory. Many people spend hours on novels and informative articles in order to acquire the much-needed theory and knowledge of the world.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">However, the education isn’t only about that, and the societies need to get the interesting and practical knowledge. In other words, the integration of theory and practical knowledge is what businesses need to ace their industry. If you look at the well-educated and experienced person, he will be able to conduct the business effectively as compared to the uneducated person. The difference in their productivity and output will be uncanny. Be it the communication or how he presented his ideas; the educated person will sport it all. Moreover, the businesses are in dire need of such personnel as they become the most valuable asset for them while inspiring everyone around them to do better.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">If we look back into the history, educational institutions were limited in the numbers, and they were only working on the aim of educating the students for the non-profit purposes. In the previous times, people weren’t passionate about acquiring an education; however, with time, people are trying to set their foot in the educational institutions. This increased the potential of people to pay attention to acquiring information, which really enhanced the level of educational institutions. With the enhanced level, the capacity and objectives of the educational institutions were enhanced.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15pt 0cm 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">Educational Businesses</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">In this modern era, the education industry has become more of a business rather than spreading education and has been adding to the economy. There is a multitude of schools, colleges, and the universities which are becoming the brand in the industry. However, these businesses are trying to expand their objective to upgrade the highest standards of education and manage the records.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">With the time changing, the educational institutions are working with the main aim to earn the profits. Making profits has become an essential thing because it’s essential to hire the professional and experienced lecturers and accountants to host the lectures. However, when the profits are concerned, the institutions need to hire the accountants to keep a record of everything and gain an understanding of the profits. However, keeping a record can be pretty challenging because there are no tangible entities involved.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">If we take a look at the generic industries such as sugar, textile, and cement industry, the accounting cycles are easy to navigate, easy to implement, and easy to keep track of. On top of all, there are multiple guidelines for them to follow to get on the right path. These industries only have to acquire the data, align them into the documents, and make a summary to report it to the higher authorities.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">As a person with accountancy expertise, it is essential to carry out the similar steps in the educational industry. However, before getting to the work, one needs to acquire the information regarding the reports, outline the data, make a summary, and report it to the senior management while following all the essential policies and regulations as posed by the educational departments of the United Kingdom. As an accountant, it is suitable to conduct an in-depth analysis of the cost, revenues, and profits to capture the market while making huge profits.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15pt 0cm 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">Our Services</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">When you come to us at MintAccountax, you need to acknowledge that we are there to help no matter what type of financial, tax, and accountancy service you need. Once we accept to handle that part of your institute for you, we will need the numbers and data to devise the reports for you. Our team of accountants has served the educational institutions in the long-run, which puts them at the liberty to help you make clear choices. Through our reports, you will be able to outline the gaps and opportunities for your business and earn the rewards through strategically-drawn plans for success and growth.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p></div>', 'Education', 'Education', '2019-09-10 22:11:15', '2021-08-17 17:43:12');
